To get started:

1) Copy settings.py.example to settings.py
2) Edit settings.py to add your MiraiEx Client ID and Secret Key and change bot parameters
3) Run it: python3 opusbot.py

Opus uses Requests which is an elegant and simple HTTP library for Python to interface with MiraiEx: https://requests.readthedocs.io/en/master/

Visit https://www.biltmore.no/miraiex/ to register yourself at MiraiEX or donate to BTC address : 3DsMZSbD286Fj1rQThPBjPXxk4dkQtVHGe to support the maintainer of this robot
